eton" lang="br" hreflang="br" class="interlanguage-link-target">Brezhoneg</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-bs"><a href="https://bs.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hermann_Hesse" title="Hermann Hesse — bosniaque" lang="bs" hreflang="bs" class="interlanguage-link-target">Bosanski</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ca"><a href="https://ca.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hermann_Hesse" title="Hermann Hesse — catalan" lang="ca" hreflang="ca" class="interlanguage-link-target">Català</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ckb"><a href="https://ckb.wikipedia.org/wiki/%DA%BE%DB%8E%D8%B1%D9%85%D8%A7%D9%86_%DA%BE%DB%8E%D8%B3%DB%95" title="ھێرمان ھێسە — sorani" lang="ckb" hreflang="ckb" class="interlanguage-link-target">کوردی</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-co"><a href="https://co.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hermann_Hesse" title="Hermann Hesse — corse" lang="co" hreflang="co" class="interlanguage-link-target">Corsu</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-cs"><a href="https://cs.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hermann_Hesse" title="Hermann Hesse — tchèque" lang="cs" hreflang="cs" class="interlanguage-link-target">Čeština</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-da"><a href="https://da.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hermann_Hesse" title="Hermann Hesse — danois" lang="da" hreflang="da" class="interlanguage-link-target">Dansk</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-de badge-Q17437796 badge-featuredarticle" title="article de qualité"><a href="https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hermann_Hesse" title="Hermann Hesse — allemand" lang="de" hreflang="de" class="interlanguage-link-target">Deutsch</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-el"><a href="https://el.wikipedia.org/wiki/%CE%88%CF%81%CE%BC%CE%B1%CE%BD_%CE%88%CF%83%CF%83%CE%B5" title="Έρμαν Έσσε — grec" lang="el" hreflang="el" class="interlanguage-link-target">Ελληνικά</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-en"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hermann_Hesse" title="Hermann Hesse — anglais" lang="en" h